Classes in de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core used by de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.api
LexicalEntry
          LexicalEntry is a class representing a lexeme in a given language.
LexicalResource
          LexicalResource is a class representing the entire resource.
Lexicon
          Lexicon is a class containing all the lexical entries of a given language within the entire resource.
Sense
          Sense is a class representing one meaning of a lexical entry.
The Sense class allows for hierarchical senses in that a sense may be more specific than another sense of the same lexical entry.
